/**
\mainpage alx : Astronomical Library eXtension 

<b>Brief description</b>\n
The alx module provides developper an astronomical function set.

<b>Detailed decription</b>\n
The module contains :
\li alxGalacticCoordinates.c - getting galactic coordinates.
\li alxMagnitude.c - computing magnitudes in all bands.
\li alxRealMagnitude.c - computing the corrected magnitude according
to the interstellar absorption.
\li alxAngularDiameter.c - computing the angular diameter of a star according
to its photometric properties.
